OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGene-therapy leap restores 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbaby girl's hearing        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A UK girl born deaf can now hear       
OL,6, unaided, after a groundbreaking        
OL,7, gene-therapy treatment.                
OL,9,FOpal Sandy was treated shortly before  
OL,10,Fher first birthday - and six months on,
OL,11,Fcan hear sounds as soft as a whisper   
OL,12,Fand is starting to talk, saying words  
OL,13,Fsuch as "Mama", "Dada" and "uh-oh".    
OL,15,FGiven as an infusion into the ear, the 
OL,16,Ftherapy replaces faulty DNA causing her
OL,17,Ftype of inherited deafness.            
OL,19,FOpal is part of a trial recruiting     
OL,20,Fpatients in the UK, US and Spain.      
